\section{Simulation Scenario}

We simulate data from this model 
\begin{eqnarray}
\nonumber Y_s \sim \sim N(\mu, \Sigma) \\
\label{s_mod}
\end{eqnarray}

The rest parameter are set as $\mu = (0,0)$, and 
\[
\Sigma = \left( \begin{array}{ccc} s  & \rho s^2 \\ 
                            \rho s^2 & s
              \end{array} \right)
\]

\section{Simulation Results}


